@andaag Thanks for the report, I noticed that bug last friday. The issue is due to the `take(1)` which prevents the trigger observable to emit more than one item. I removed it here 2455bcf21d5ac9adc82e6f89786d6de2a085b89c but now I have to fix the `request` method which doesn't work any more. 

